Program: Crossing Continents
Title: The Children of Dushanbe
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00rjz1p
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 29 Mar 2010
Angus Crawford reports on efforts to rescue vulnerable girls in Tajikistan who were locked up rather than helped. He hears how girls who had been raped were detained for being 'degenerate'. He also sees how a British NGO is working with the Tajik authorities to help these teenagers find freedom and safety. Show less